===決賽周抽籤===
2011年12月2日在[[烏克蘭|烏克蘭]][[基輔|基輔]]的「烏克蘭藝術博物館」（National Palace of Arts "Ukraina"）舉行抽籤儀式<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro2012/news/newsid=1692248.html |title=December date for EURO finals draw in Kyiv |work=[[UEFA|UEFA]] |date=3 October 2011 |accessdate=2011-12-03 |archive-date=2011-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111005154953/http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro2012/news/newsid=1692248.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/news/newsid=1725325.html |title=EURO draw throws up fascinating group tests |work=[[UEFA|UEFA]] |date=2 December 2011 |accessdate=2011-12-03 |archive-date=2012-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120618000046/http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/news/newsid=1725325.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

與2004年及2008年的決賽週相同，16支參賽球隊按[[欧洲足联积分排名|欧洲足联积分排名]]被分為4個檔次分組<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.uefa.com/MultimediaFiles/Download/competitions/General/01/69/56/52/1695652_DOWNLOAD.pdf |title=UEFA's national team coefficient ranking |work=[[UEFA|UEFA]] |date=16 November 2011 |accessdate=2011-12-03 |archive-date=2015-12-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151213065100/http://www.uefa.com/MultimediaFiles/Download/competitions/General/01/69/56/52/1695652_DOWNLOAD.pdf |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而作為聯合主辦國，波蘭和烏克蘭獲自動置於第一組，同組還有衛冕冠軍西班牙<ref name="Seedings">{{cite news |url=http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/news/newsid=1716622.html |title=EURO finals draw seedings unveiled |work=[[UEFA|UEFA]] |date=16 November 2011 |accessdate=2011-12-03 |archive-date=2012-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120627164707/http://www.uefa.com/uefaeuro/news/newsid=1716622.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在抽籤過程中，分組賽每個小組各有一隊來自四個不同的檔次分組。同時亦會決定由第二至第四檔次分組的席次（例如 A2、A3或A4）以編制賽程<ref name="Seedings"/>。為方便安排，波蘭獲預早編為A1，而烏克蘭則為D1<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.uefa.com/uefa/aboutuefa/organisation/executivecommittee/news/newsid=1543454.html |title=Fixture plan brings EURO dream closer |work=[[UEFA|UEFA]] |date=4 October 2010 |accessdate=2011-12-03 |archive-date=2013-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130528100542/http://www.uefa.com/uefa/aboutuefa/organisation/executivecommittee/news/newsid=1543454.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，代表荷蘭和西班牙只能夠取得B1或C1。

